text: Cymbula compressa is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Patellidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== ==External links== Cymbula compressa, museum specimen Naturalis Category:Patellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1758 Category:Taxa named by Carl Linnaeus
title: Cymbula compressa
